<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>After trying to understand the theory of operation and internal details about Zend_Tool, I've seen that Zend_Tool_Project_Provider_ProjectProvider doesn't allows usage of "--pretend" flag to see what will be created.
After looking on the source code, I've noticed that this class doens't implement "Zend_Tool_Framework_Provider_Pretendable" wich is necessary to enabled "--pretend" flag.</p>

